                                            <p class="pt-000000c51c6111-b007-475d-99b0-6435c5bf5adb" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span class="pt-000001c51c6111-b007-475d-99b0-6435c5bf5adb"><img src="data:image/png;base64," style="width: 1.38314in;height: 0.9791667in;" alt="Picture 1" /></span><style>span { white-space: pre-wrap; }p.pt-000000c51c6111-b007-475d-99b0-6435c5bf5adb {line-height: 108%;margin-top: 0;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;margin-bottom: 0;}span.pt-000001c51c6111-b007-475d-99b0-6435c5bf5adb {font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;margin: 0;padding: 0;}</style></p><p class="pt-00000011c55798-8e66-4def-9218-e3feccd2b947" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span class="pt-00000111c55798-8e66-4def-9218-e3feccd2b947">GLb</span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-00000111c55798-8e66-4def-9218-e3feccd2b947">, </span><span class="math-tex" style="font-family: Cambria Math !important;" xmlns="">\({m}_{0}{c}^{2}=m{c}^{2}+m{c}^{2}⇒{m}_{0}=2m\) </span><style>span { white-space: pre-wrap; }p.pt-00000011c55798-8e66-4def-9218-e3feccd2b947 {line-height: 108%;margin-top: 0;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;margin-bottom: 0;}span.pt-00000111c55798-8e66-4def-9218-e3feccd2b947 {font-family: SutonnyMJ;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;margin: 0;padding: 0;}</style></p><p class="pt-0000002aeaf5dc-dce6-4b75-892e-72d99921790f" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span class="math-tex" style="font-family: Cambria Math !important;" xmlns="">\(⇒{m}_{0}=2\times \frac{{m}_{0}^{{'}}}{\sqrt{1-\frac{{v}^{2}}{{c}^{2}}}}=2\times \frac{{m}_{0}^{{'}}}{\sqrt{1-{\left(\frac{1}{2}\right)}^{2}}}=2\times {m}_{0}^{{'}}\times \frac{2}{\sqrt{3}}\) </span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-0000012aeaf5dc-dce6-4b75-892e-72d99921790f"> </span><style>span { white-space: pre-wrap; }p.pt-0000002aeaf5dc-dce6-4b75-892e-72d99921790f {line-height: 108%;margin-top: 0;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;margin-bottom: 0;}span.pt-0000012aeaf5dc-dce6-4b75-892e-72d99921790f {font-family: Sutonny