                                            <p class="pt-00000044ce2f2a-3e75-4f43-a532-2a3d4f8b888f" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span class="pt-00000144ce2f2a-3e75-4f43-a532-2a3d4f8b888f">Correctly rewrite the sentences provided below.</span><style>span { white-space: pre-wrap; }p.pt-00000044ce2f2a-3e75-4f43-a532-2a3d4f8b888f {line-height: 108%;margin-top: 0;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;margin-bottom: 0;}span.pt-00000144ce2f2a-3e75-4f43-a532-2a3d4f8b888f {font-family: Times New Roman;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;margin: 0;padding: 0;}</style></p><p class="pt-000000c4504f19-f607-4772-a1ec-4094a914a5c3" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span class="pt-000001c4504f19-f607-4772-a1ec-4094a914a5c3">(a) He resembles with his father.</span><style>span { white-space: pre-wrap; }p.pt-000000c4504f19-f607-4772-a1ec-4094a914a5c3 {line-height: 108%;margin-top: 0;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;margin-bottom: 0;}span.pt-000001c4504f19-f607-4772-a1ec-4094a914a5c3 {font-family: Times New Roman;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;margin: 0;padding: 0;}</style></p><p class="pt-00000042630dde-62d0-4309-aeca-4b02ed30902e" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span class="pt-00000142630dde-62d0-4309-aeca-4b02ed30902e">(b) She is my cousin sister.</span><style>span { white-space: pre-wrap; }p.pt-00000042630dde-62d0-4309-aeca-4b02ed30902e {line-height: 108%;margin-top: 0;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;margin-bottom: 0;}span.pt-00000142630dde-62d0-4309-aeca-4b02ed30902e {font-family: Times New Roman;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;margin: 0;padding: 0;}</style></p><p class="pt-000000dc46b693-d420-4610-9e38-ea4efb1ea2e5" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span class="pt-000001dc46b693-d420-4610-9e38-ea4efb1ea2e5">(c) He is more preferable than her.</span><style>span { white-space: pre-wrap; }p.pt-000000dc46b693-d420-4610-9e38-ea4efb1ea2e5 {line-height: 108%;margin-top: 0;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;margin-bottom: 0;}span.pt-000001dc46b693-d420-4610-9e