                                        <div class="row solveText" style=" display: block; padding:10px; color:#077307; overflow-x: auto; background-color: #d7f7d4; ">
                                            <p class="pt-000000f718a986-3c12-489c-89f3-11996b98df62" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span class="pt-000001f718a986-3c12-489c-89f3-11996b98df62">(a) He resembles his father.</span><style>span { white-space: pre-wrap; }p.pt-000000f718a986-3c12-489c-89f3-11996b98df62 {line-height: 108%;margin-top: 0;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;margin-bottom: 0;}span.pt-000001f718a986-3c12-489c-89f3-11996b98df62 {font-family: Times New Roman;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;margin: 0;padding: 0;}</style></p><p class="pt-000000f4912e0e-2fef-455c-9787-4b85d0f72c16" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span class="pt-000001f4912e0e-2fef-455c-9787-4b85d0f72c16">(b) She is my cousin/sister.</span><style>span { white-space: pre-wrap; }p.pt-000000f4912e0e-2fef-455c-9787-4b85d0f72c16 {line-height: 108%;margin-top: 0;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;margin-bottom: 0;}span.pt-000001f4912e0e-2fef-455c-9787-4b85d0f72c16 {font-family: Times New Roman;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;margin: 0;padding: 0;}</style></p><p class="pt-00000025ea677f-b723-490b-a374-a95eadcc7452" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span class="pt-00000125ea677f-b723-490b-a374-a95eadcc7452">(c) He is preferable to her.</span><style>span { white-space: pre-wrap; }p.pt-00000025ea677f-b723-490b-a374-a95eadcc7452 {line-height: 108%;margin-top: 0;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;margin-bottom: 0;}span.pt-00000125ea677f-b723-490b-a374-a95eadcc7452 {font-family: Times New Roman;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;margin: 0;padding: 0;}</style></p><p class="pt-0000009023b918-79e6-43ed-b43b-6824a1aa5a68" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-0000019023b918-79e6-43ed-b43b-6824a1aa5a68">(d) The wages of sin </span><span class="pt-0000019023b918-79e6-43ed-b43b-6824a1aa5a68">is</span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-0000019023b918-79e6-43ed-b43b-6824a1aa5a68"> death.</span><style>span { white-space: pre-wrap; }p.pt-0000009023b918-79e6-43ed-b43b-6824a1aa5a68 {line-height: 108%;margin-top: 0;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;margin-bottom: 0;}span.pt-0000019023b918-79e6-43ed-b43b-6824a1aa5a68 {font-family: Times New Roman;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;margin: 0;padding: 0;}</style></p><p class="pt-00000027fca84d-995f-44a0-977b-175863b8a35a" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span class="pt-00000127fca84d-995f-44a0-977b-175863b8a35a">(e) He goes abroad.</span><style>span { white-space: pre-wrap; }p.pt-00000027fca84d-995f-44a0-977b-175863b8a35a {line-height: 108%;margin-top: 0;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;margin-bottom: 0;}span.pt-00000127fca84d-995f-44a0-977b-175863b8a35a {font-family: Times New Roman;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;margin: 0;padding: 0;}</style></p><p class="pt-000000a16509c9-4f35-4106-9c7b-9f06ca23fb73" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span class="pt-000001a16509c9-4f35-4106-9c7b-9f06ca23fb73">Marks Distribution:</span><style>span { white-space: pre-wrap; }p.pt-000000a16509c9-4f35-4106-9c7b-9f06ca23fb73 {line-height: 108%;margin-top: 0;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;margin-bottom: 0;}span.pt-000001a16509c9-4f35-4106-9c7b-9f06ca23fb73 {font-family: Times New Roman;font-style: normal;font-weight: bold;margin: 0;padding: 0;}</style></p><p class="pt-0000000eb23622-c235-43e0-9964-9a5e8c77383b" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span class="pt-0000010eb23622-c235-43e0-9964-9a5e8c77383b">(0.5</span><span class="math-tex" style="font-family: Cambria Math !important;" xmlns="">\(\times \) </span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-0000020eb23622-c235-43e0-9964-9a5e8c77383b"> </span><span class="pt-0000010eb23622-c235-43e0-9964-9a5e8c77383b">5) =2.5 marks for</span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-0000020eb23622-c235-43e0-9964-9a5e8c77383b"> </span><span class="pt-0000010eb23622-c235-43e0-9964-9a5e8c77383b">re-write the correct form of the following sentences</span><style>span { white-space: pre-wrap; }p.pt-0000000eb23622-c235-43e0-9964-9a5e8c77383b {line-height: 108%;margin-top: 0;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;margin-bottom: 0;}span.pt-0000010eb23622-c235-43e0-9964-9a5e8c77383b {font-family: Times New Roman;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;margin: 0;padding: 0;}span.pt-0000020eb23622-c235-43e0-9964-9a5e8c77383b {font-family: Times New Roman;font-style: normal;font-weight: bold;margin: 0;padding: 0;}</style></p>
