                                        <div class="questionText" style="display: block;">
                                            <p class="pt-000000c5dd1ee4-d5fe-4831-9864-e75c8078757b" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span class="pt-000001c5dd1ee4-d5fe-4831-9864-e75c8078757b">Explain the following words within one sentence.</span><style>span { white-space: pre-wrap; }p.pt-000000c5dd1ee4-d5fe-4831-9864-e75c8078757b {margin-bottom: 0;line-height: 108%;margin-top: 0;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;}span.pt-000001c5dd1ee4-d5fe-4831-9864-e75c8078757b {font-family: Times New Roman;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;margin: 0;padding: 0;}</style></p><p class="pt-000000b20c47c7-bb03-4d7a-9eb1-e2ac0de26aa2" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span class="pt-000001b20c47c7-bb03-4d7a-9eb1-e2ac0de26aa2">Archeologist, Botanist, Ambivert, Astronomer, Hostage</span><style>span { white-space: pre-wrap; }p.pt-000000b20c47c7-bb03-4d7a-9eb1-e2ac0de26aa2 {margin-bottom: 0;line-height: 108%;margin-top: 0;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;}span.pt-000001b20c47c7-bb03-4d7a-9eb1-e2ac0de26aa2 {font-family: Times New Roman;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;margin: 0;padding: 0;}</style></p>
