                                            <p class="pt-0000006d88b225-2b49-4d1a-ae50-514f544cc834" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span class="pt-0000016d88b225-2b49-4d1a-ae50-514f544cc834">Archeologist</span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-0000026d88b225-2b49-4d1a-ae50-514f544cc834"> – A scientist who studies ancient remains and artifacts.</span><style>span { white-space: pre-wrap; }p.pt-0000006d88b225-2b49-4d1a-ae50-514f544cc834 {margin-bottom: 0;line-height: 108%;margin-top: 0;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;}span.pt-0000016d88b225-2b49-4d1a-ae50-514f544cc834 {font-family: Times New Roman;font-style: normal;font-weight: bold;margin: 0;padding: 0;}span.pt-0000026d88b225-2b49-4d1a-ae50-514f544cc834 {font-family: Times New Roman;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;margin: 0;padding: 0;}</style></p><p class="pt-000000617dae08-d687-466f-84fb-976dc0b6d11e" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span class="pt-000001617dae08-d687-466f-84fb-976dc0b6d11e">Botanist</span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-000002617dae08-d687-466f-84fb-976dc0b6d11e"> – A scientist who studies plants.</span><style>span { white-space: pre-wrap; }p.pt-000000617dae08-d687-466f-84fb-976dc0b6d11e {margin-bottom: 0;line-height: 108%;margin-top: 0;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;}span.pt-000001617dae08-d687-466f-84fb-976dc0b6d11e {font-family: Times New Roman;font-style: normal;font-weight: bold;margin: 0;padding: 0;}span.pt-000002617dae08-d687-466f-84fb-976dc0b6d11e {font-family: Times New Roman;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;margin: 0;padding: 0;}</style></p><p class="pt-0000005634761e-9014-46b2-b1c8-2da414b700fd" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span class="pt-0000015634761e-9014-46b2-b1c8-2da414b700fd">Ambivert</span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-0000025634761e-9014-46b2-b1c8-2da414b700fd"> – A person with both introvert and extrovert traits.</span><style>span { white-space: pre-wrap; }p.pt-0000005634761e-9014-46b2-b1c8-2da414b700fd {margin-bottom: 0;line-height: 108%;margin-top: 0;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;}span.pt-0000015634761e-9014-46b2-b1c8-2da414b700fd {font-family: Times New Roman;font-style: normal;font-weight: bold;margin: 0;padding: 0;}span.pt-0000025634761e-9014-46b2-b1c8-2da414b700fd {font-family: Times New Roman;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;margin: 0;padding: 0;}</style></p><p class="pt-000000efb90f89-c3b1-4bdf-b8fc-2a6d53040fea" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span class="pt-000001efb90f89-c3b1-4bdf-b8fc-2a6d53040fea">Astronomer</span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-000002efb90f89-c3b1-4bdf-b8fc-2a6d53040fea"> – A scientist who studies stars and planets.</span><style>span { white-space: pre-wrap; }p.pt-000000efb90f89-c3b1-4bdf-b8fc-2a6d53040fea {margin-bottom: 0;line-height: 108%;margin-top: 0;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;}span.pt-000001efb90f89-c3b1-4bdf-b8fc-2a6d53040fea {font-family: Times New Roman;font-style: normal;font-weight: bold;margin: 0;padding: 0;}span.pt-000002efb90f89-c3b1-4bdf-b8fc-2a6d53040fea {font-family: Times New Roman;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;margin: 0;padding: 0;}</style></p><p class="pt-000000672dba73-af42-4531-bfc2-ff58a629d8f2" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span class="pt-000001672dba73-af42-4531-bfc2-ff58a629d8f2">Hostage</span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-000002672dba73-af42-4531-bfc2-ff58a629d8f2"> – A person seized and held as security.</span><style>span { white-space: pre-wrap; }p.pt-000000672dba73-af42-4531-bfc2-ff58a629d8f2 {margin-bottom: 0;line-height: 108%;margin-top: 0;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;}span.pt-000001672dba73-af42-4531-bfc2-ff58a629d8f2 {font-family: Times New Roman;font-style: normal;font-weight: bold;margin: 0;padding: 0;}span.pt-000002672dba73-af42-4531-bfc2-ff58a629d8f2 {font-family: Times New Roman;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;margin: 0;padding: 0;}</style></p><p class="pt-000000d6f27c4e-b1e3-4142-b266-291b55972471" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span class="pt-000001d6f27c4e-b1e3-4142-b266-291b55972471">Marks Distribution:</span><style>span { white-space: pre-wrap; }p.pt-000000d6f27c4e-b1e3-4142-b266-291b55972471 {margin-bottom: 0;line-height: 108%;margin-top: 0;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;}span.pt-000001d6f27c4e-b1e3-4142-b266-291b55972471 {font-family: Times New Roman;font-style: normal;font-weight: bold;margin: 0;padding: 0;}</style></p><p class="pt-000000524887c4-e327-4ae1-b957-e51a8a1cdc6f" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span class="pt-000001524887c4-e327-4ae1-b957-e51a8a1cdc6f">(0.5</span><span class="math-tex" style="font-family: Cambria Math !important;" xmlns="">\(\times \) </span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-000002524887c4-e327-4ae1-b957-e51a8a1cdc6f"> </span><span class="pt-000001524887c4-e327-4ae1-b957-e51a8a1cdc6f">5) =2.5 marks for</span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-000002524887c4-e327-4ae1-b957-e51a8a1cdc6f"> </span><span class="pt-000001524887c4-e327-4ae1-b957-e51a8a1cdc6f">Explain within one sentence</span><span class="pt-000002524887c4-e327-4ae1-b957-e51a8a1cdc6f">.</span><style>span { white-space: pre-wrap; }p.pt-000000524887c4-e327-4ae1-b957-e51a8a1cdc6f {margin-bottom: 0;line-height: 108%;margin-top: 0;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;}span.pt-000001524887c4-e327-4ae1-b957-e51a8a1cdc6f {font-family: Times New Roman;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;margin: 0;padding: 0;}span.pt-000002524887c4-e327-4ae1-b957-e51a8a1cdc6f {font-family: Times New Roman;font-style: normal;font-weight: bold;margin: 0;padding: 0;}</style></p><p class="pt-00000048f9f393-985b-44e6-967f-69bcc1397de0" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><style>span { white-space: pre-wrap; }p.pt-00000048f9f393-985b-44e6-967f-69bcc1397de0 {margin-bottom: 0;line-height: 108%;margin-top: 0;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;}</style></p>
