                        <div class="row questionBlock">
                            <div class="row question">
                                <div class="col-md-12" style="padding-left:0px; padding-right:0px;">
                                    <div class="row">
                                        <div class="serial">
                                            <span>Question 22</span>
                                        </div>
                                        <div class="questionText" style="display: block;">
                                            <p class="pt-0000000541ad86-ea0d-4487-84e1-ae7ab88a578b" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span class="pt-0000010541ad86-ea0d-4487-84e1-ae7ab88a578b">Write a paragraph on ‘</span><span class="pt-0000020541ad86-ea0d-4487-84e1-ae7ab88a578b">Youth and Entrepreneurship in Bangladesh’</span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-0000010541ad86-ea0d-4487-84e1-ae7ab88a578b"> within 100 words.</span><style>span { white-space: pre-wrap; }p.pt-0000000541ad86-ea0d-4487-84e1-ae7ab88a578b {line-height: 108%;margin-top: 0;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;margin-bottom: 0;}span.pt-0000010541ad86-ea0d-4487-84e1-ae7ab88a578b {font-family: Times New Roman;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;margin: 0;padding: 0;}span.pt-0000020541ad86-ea0d-4487-84e1-ae7ab88a578b {font-family: Times New Roman;font-style: normal;font-weight: bold;margin: 0;padding: 0;}</style></p>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                        <div class="row solveText" style=" display: block; padding:10px; color:#077307; overflow-x: auto; background-color: #d7f7d4; ">
                                            <p class="pt-0000008c5c5ecf-ce2a-4289-ad28-d30f9dacb4dd" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span class="pt-0000018c5c5ecf-ce2a-4289-ad28-d30f9dacb4dd">Youth and Entrepreneurship in Bangladesh</span><style>span { white-space: pre-wrap; }p.pt-0000008c5c5ecf-ce2a-4289-ad28-d30f9dacb4dd {text-align: center;line-height: 108%;margin-top: 0;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;margin-bottom: 0;}span.pt-0000018c5c5ecf-ce2a-4289-ad28-d30f9dacb4dd {font-family: Times New Roman;font-style: normal;font-weight: bold;margin: 0;padding: 0;}</style></p><p class="pt-0000001a0f2353-23b2-4116-b490-92f85b8b33db" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span class="pt-0000011a0f2353-23b2-4116-b490-92f85b8b33db">Youth entrepre</span><span class="pt-0000011a0f2353-23b2-4116-b490-92f85b8b33db">neurship in Bangladesh is a transformative force, driving economic growth and innovation. With a growing emphasis on digital skills, Bangladeshi youth are increasingly venturing into technology, e-commerce and social enterprises, capitalizing on the countr</span><span class="pt-0000011a0f2353-23b2-4116-b490-92f85b8b33db">y&#39;s rapid internet expansion. Government initiatives and support from organizations like Startup Bangladesh offer funding and mentorship, nurturing young entrepreneurs. However, challenges such as limited access to finance, inadequate infrastructure, and b</span><span class="pt-0000011a0f2353-23b2-4116-b490-92f85b8b33db">ureaucratic hurdles persist. Overcoming these barriers is essential for empowering the youth to create sustainable businesses, contributing to job creation and poverty reduction, and positioning Bangladesh as a hub for entrepreneurial talent in South Asia.</span><style>span { white-space: pre-wrap; }p.pt-0000001a0f2353-23b2-4116-b490-92f85b8b33db {line-height: 108%;margin-top: 0;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;margin-bottom: 0;}span.pt-0000011a0f2353-23b2-4116-b490-92f85b8b33db {font-family: Times New Roman;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;margin: 0;padding: 0;}</style></p><p class="pt-000000bfb90495-8840-4efd-a197-c0aa1b7b9969" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span class="pt-000001bfb90495-8840-4efd-a197-c0aa1b7b9969">Marks Distribution:</span><style>span { white-space: pre-wrap; }p.pt-000000bfb90495-8840-4efd-a197-c0aa1b7b9969 {line-height: 108%;margin-top: 0;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;margin-bottom: 0;}span.pt-000001bfb90495-8840-4efd-a197-c0aa1b7b9969 {font-family: Times New Roman;font-style: normal;font-weight: bold;margin: 0;padding: 0;}</style></p><p class="pt-000000b1334450-e677-424e-afe0-449b9989b588" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span class="pt-000001b1334450-e677-424e-afe0-449b9989b588">0.5 mark for writing the Title, “Youth and Entrepreneurship in Bangladesh’’</span><style>span { white-space: pre-wrap; }p.pt-000000b1334450-e677-424e-afe0-449b9989b588 {line-height: 108%;margin-top: 0;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;margin-bottom: 0;}span.pt-000001b1334450-e677-424e-afe0-449b9989b588 {font-family: Times New Roman;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;margin: 0;padding: 0;}</style></p><p class="pt-000000ae53fa31-2df5-4a5a-bdca-bb42286bd301" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span class="pt-000001ae53fa31-2df5-4a5a-bdca-bb42286bd301">1.5 marks for writing Youth entrepreneurship in Bangladesh is a transformative force, driving economic growth and innovation.</span><style>span { white-space: pre-wrap; }p.pt-000000ae53fa31-2df5-4a5a-bdca-bb42286bd301 {line-height: 108%;margin-top: 0;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;margin-bottom: 0;}span.pt-000001ae53fa31-2df5-4a5a-bdca-bb42286bd301 {font-family: Times New Roman;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;margin: 0;padding: 0;}</style></p><p class="pt-000000ff2874c2-07cd-4407-a30e-d29f25b90b1a" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span class="pt-000001ff2874c2-07cd-4407-a30e-d29f25b90b1a">1.5 marks for writing Bangladeshi youth are increasingly venturing into technology, e-commerce and social enterprises, capitalizing on the country&#39;s rapid internet expansion</span><style>span { white-space: pre-wrap; }p.pt-000000ff2874c2-07cd-4407-a30e-d29f25b90b1a {line-height: 108%;margin-top: 0;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;margin-bottom: 0;}span.pt-000001ff2874c2-07cd-4407-a30e-d29f25b90b1a {font-family: Times New Roman;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;margin: 0;padding: 0;}</style></p><p class="pt-0000002a91decc-dd81-48f9-9203-82bbeeaf6dad" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-0000012a91decc-dd81-48f9-9203-82bbeeaf6dad">1.5 marks for writing Overcoming these barriers is essential for empowering the youth to create sustainable </span><span class="pt-0000012a91decc-dd81-48f9-9203-82bbeeaf6dad">businesses, contributing to job creation and poverty reduction, and positioning Bangladesh as a hub for entrepreneurial talent in South Asia.</span><style>span { white-space: pre-wrap; }p.pt-0000002a91decc-dd81-48f9-9203-82bbeeaf6dad {line-height: 108%;margin-top: 0;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;margin-bottom: 0;}span.pt-0000012a91decc-dd81-48f9-9203-82bbeeaf6dad {font-family: Times New Roman;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;margin: 0;padding: 0;}</style></p><p class="pt-000000cbd84bb0-455b-43c4-bab4-bc988c7f7136" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span class="pt-000001cbd84bb0-455b-43c4-bab4-bc988c7f7136">[</span><span class="pt-000002cbd84bb0-455b-43c4-bab4-bc988c7f7136">Instructions:</span><style>span { white-space: pre-wrap; }p.pt-000000cbd84bb0-455b-43c4-bab4-bc988c7f7136 {line-height: 108%;margin-top: 0;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;margin-bottom: 0;}span.pt-000001cbd84bb0-455b-43c4-bab4-bc988c7f7136 {font-family: Times New Roman;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;margin: 0;padding: 0;}span.pt-000002cbd84bb0-455b-43c4-bab4-bc988c7f7136 {font-family: Times New Roman;font-style: normal;font-weight: bold;margin: 0;padding: 0;}</style></p><p class="pt-00000028e1e7f1-3b7e-4c9a-a700-1bd9639678bf" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-00000128e1e7f1-3b7e-4c9a-a700-1bd9639678bf">* Students must write it within one single para. If it becomes </span><span class="pt-00000228e1e7f1-3b7e-4c9a-a700-1bd9639678bf">more than one para</span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-00000128e1e7f1-3b7e-4c9a-a700-1bd9639678bf">, </span><span class="pt-00000228e1e7f1-3b7e-4c9a-a700-1bd9639678bf">50% marks</span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-00000128e1e7f1-3b7e-4c9a-a700-1bd9639678bf"> have to be </span><span class="pt-00000228e1e7f1-3b7e-4c9a-a700-1bd9639678bf">deducted</span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-00000128e1e7f1-3b7e-4c9a-a700-1bd9639678bf"> from the </span><span class="pt-00000228e1e7f1-3b7e-4c9a-a700-1bd9639678bf">obtained marks.</span><style>span { white-space: pre-wrap; }p.pt-00000028e1e7f1-3b7e-4c9a-a700-1bd9639678bf {line-height: 108%;margin-top: 0;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;margin-bottom: 0;}span.pt-00000128e1e7f1-3b7e-4c9a-a700-1bd9639678bf {font-family: Times New Roman;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;margin: 0;padding: 0;}span.pt-00000228e1e7f1-3b7e-4c9a-a700-1bd9639678bf {font-family: Times New Roman;font-style: normal;font-weight: bold;margin: 0;padding: 0;}</style></p><p class="pt-000000e836dc38-5a76-418b-afe2-92c8397e4b4d" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-000001e836dc38-5a76-418b-afe2-92c8397e4b4d">* </span><span class="pt-000002e836dc38-5a76-418b-afe2-92c8397e4b4d">Students must write it within 100 words limit.</span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-000001e836dc38-5a76-418b-afe2-92c8397e4b4d"> </span><span class="pt-000002e836dc38-5a76-418b-afe2-92c8397e4b4d">For exceeding the</span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-000001e836dc38-5a76-418b-afe2-92c8397e4b4d"> 100 words limit, 0.5 mark</span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-000002e836dc38-5a76-418b-afe2-92c8397e4b4d"> have to be </span><span class="pt-000001e836dc38-5a76-418b-afe2-92c8397e4b4d">deducted</span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-000002e836dc38-5a76-418b-afe2-92c8397e4b4d"> from the </span><span class="pt-000001e836dc38-5a76-418b-afe2-92c8397e4b4d">deserved marks.</span><style>span { white-space: pre-wrap; }p.pt-000000e836dc38-5a76-418b-afe2-92c8397e4b4d {line-height: 108%;margin-top: 0;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;margin-bottom: 0;}span.pt-000001e836dc38-5a76-418b-afe2-92c8397e4b4d {font-family: Times New Roman;font-style: normal;font-weight: bold;margin: 0;padding: 0;}span.pt-000002e836dc38-5a76-418b-afe2-92c8397e4b4d {font-family: Times New Roman;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;margin: 0;padding: 0;}</style></p><p class="pt-000000620ec61f-32c9-4afc-8d31-3c23524ba0a6" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-000001620ec61f-32c9-4afc-8d31-3c23524ba0a6">* 0.5 mark will be </span><span class="pt-000002620ec61f-32c9-4afc-8d31-3c23524ba0a6">deducted for one or two grammar or spelling mistakes</span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-000001620ec61f-32c9-4afc-8d31-3c23524ba0a6">, 01 mark </span><span class="pt-000002620ec61f-32c9-4afc-8d31-3c23524ba0a6">for three or more grammar or spelling mistakes.</span><style>span { white-space: pre-wrap; }p.pt-000000620ec61f-32c9-4afc-8d31-3c23524ba0a6 {line-height: 108%;margin-top: 0;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;margin-bottom: 0;}span.pt-000001620ec61f-32c9-4afc-8d31-3c23524ba0a6 {font-family: Times New Roman;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;margin: 0;padding: 0;}span.pt-000002620ec61f-32c9-4afc-8d31-3c23524ba0a6 {font-family: Times New Roman;font-style: normal;font-weight: bold;margin: 0;padding: 0;}</style></p>
                                        </div>
